# VibeIDE local-only paths (keep out of git)
# Policy contract — see references/v1/docs-policy.md (also local-only):
#   - docs/ is **fully** ignored — public docs go in the website repo, not here.
#   - references/* is local-only normative documentation for maintainers.
#   - Only references/logo-final.png is committed (used by README).
# Anything published to the public site lives elsewhere; nothing under docs/
# or references/ is part of the source tree contract.
references/*
!references/logo-final.png
CLAUDE.md
.cursor/
.vibe/
.agents/
.config/
docs/
# Root bin/: ignore local scratch by default; allow selected committed utilities (see script-save / knowledge.md)
bin/*
!bin/vibe-language-pack-nls.mjs
# Note: do not add `.github/` here — CI, issue templates, and agent docs must remain committable.

# Local IDE / OS noise (keep out of public tree)
.idea/

builds/

# VSCodeSync local cache (not source of truth)
.vscode/vscodesync.json
